P1.9 VPC CIDR Configuration implementation:
- VpcCIDR in planInfraInput (default 10.0.0.0/16)
- VpcCIDR persisted in state.Plan
- ValidateVpcCIDR() validates prefix /16 to /24
- CalculateSubnetLayout() derives subnet CIDRs
- provisionVPC uses dynamic subnet layout
- Tests: TestValidateVpcCIDR, TestCalculateSubnetLayout, TestPlanInfra_VpcCIDR

Enables custom VPC CIDR for VPC peering scenarios.
